raw_data.title: Coach
raw_data.description: Designs, plans and delivers individual or group coaching to achieve desired results for customer and their organization. Works with client to help identify strengths and weaknesses, and ultimately optimize the individual’s performance and leadership. Examples of the results that can be achieved with a Coach are improved planning for high-priority issues, directing skills development, meeting team performance goals, establishing greater credibility, prioritization best practices, creating personal and team balance between work and personal life, improving communication skills, and effective goal setting. Collects data to assess organizational challenges, opportunities and threats as perceived by client. Conducts interviews  as well as a logical examination of documentation and other information to clarify a thorough understanding of the issues. Communicates information regarding themes and data analysis.
